forohfor.scryfall.api

Class Card

  • java.lang.Object
    • forohfor.scryfall.api.Card

  • public class Card
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a single printing of one card. "Special" cards (transforming/meld cards, for instance), will have one Card object for each state of the card.
    Author:
    ForOhForError

        public java.util.ArrayList<CardReference> getPartReferences()
